::Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Reptilica and Bloodystrike enter the lab, carrying the shivering femmbot 
between them. It was warm, all the devices generating a bit of heat. They 
manage to get her up on the table, strapping her down. After how Feline broke 
out, they use reinforced metal straps, strapping her neck, legs, and arms. 
The two bots stand at either side of the table, their eyes feasting on the 
femmbot before them.

They both reach out to touch her at the same time, stiffening as each one 
sees the other move. Reptilica and Bloodystrike glare hostilly at each other, 
their hands retreating. They both stand over the femm, glaring at each other. 
Reptilica activates his comm-link, not taking his eyes off his 'friend'.

"Zardus, she's in the lab," he says into it, "We're ready when you are."
